-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
--! создать пользователя post запросом
1)click new
2) select HTTP Request
3) select POST
4) fill in URL  https://reqres.in//api/users
5) click Body 
6) select in Body options "raw"
7) celect JSON format
8) fill field
 {
    "name": "morpheus",
    "job": "leader"
}
9) click button "send"

Response  code 201

{
    "name": "morpheus",
    "job": "leader",
    "id": "913",
    "createdAt": "2022-02-06T11:24:57.950Z"
}
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

--! Зарегистрироватся успешный кейс
1) click new
2) select HTTP Request
3) select POST
4) fill in URL https://reqres.in/api/register
5) click Body 
6) select in Body options "raw"
7) celect JSON format
8) fill field 
{
    "email": "eve.holt@reqres.in",
    "password": "pistol"
}
9) click button "send"

Response: code 200

{
    "id": 4,
    "token": "QpwL5tke4Pnpja7X4"
}
--------------------------------------------
--! пройти автроизацию
1) click new
2) select HTTP Request
3) select POST
4) fill in URL hthttps://reqres.in/api/login
5) click Body 
6) select in Body options "raw"
7) celect JSON format
8) fill field 
{
    "email": "eve.holt@reqres.in",
    "password": "cityslicka"
}
9) click button "send"
Respone :code 200

{
    "token": "QpwL5tke4Pnpja7X4"
}


